        <p>This infographic synthesizes key insights from Robbins & Judge's "Organizational Behavior, 19th Ed."</p>
        <p class="text-sm mt-2 opacity-75">Visualizations created with Chart.js and Tailwind CSS. No SVG or Mermaid JS used.</p>
